<tr valign="top" id="mwTg">
<td id="mwTw">• "the need for the meditator to retrain his attention, whether through concentration or mindfulness, is the single invariant ingredient in... every meditation system"<sup about="#mwt96" class="mw-ref" id="cite_ref-goleman88_4-3" rel="dc:references" typeof="mw:Extension/ref" data-mw='{"name":"ref","attrs":{"name":"goleman88"}}'><a href="./Meditation#cite_note-goleman88-4" style="counter-reset: mw-Ref 4;"><span class="mw-reflink-text">[4]</span></a></sup><sup class="reference" style="white-space:nowrap;" about="#mwt94" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"rp","href":"./Template:Rp"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"107"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwUA">:<span>107</span></sup></td>
