andi%2C+Muhammad+Nazim+Adil+al-Haqqani&amp;rft.au=Kabbani%2C+Muhammad+Hisham&amp;rft.au=Mirahmadi%2C+Hedieh&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.loc.gov%2Fcatdir%2Ftoc%2Fecip057%2F2005001975.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMeditation" class="Z3988" about="#mwt52" id="mwA_E"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt52" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwA_I"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-carroll05-18" id="cite_note-carroll05-18"><a href="./Meditation#cite_ref-carroll05_18-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-carroll05-18" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation journal" about="#mwt57" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Cite journal ","href":"./Template:Cite_journal"},"params":{"author":{"wt":"Mary Carroll"},"year":{"wt":"2005"},"title":{"wt":"Divine therapy: Teaching reflective and meditative practices"},"journal":{"wt":"Teaching Theology and Religion"},"volume":{"wt":"8"},"issue":{"wt":"4"},"pages":{"wt":"232–38"},"url":{"wt":""},"doi":{"wt":"10.1111/j.1467-9647.2005.00249.x"},"pmid":{"wt":""}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwA_M">Mary Carroll (2005). "Divine therapy: Teaching reflective and meditative practices". <i id="mwA_Q">Teaching Theology and Religion</i>. <b id="mwA_U">8</b> (4): 232–38. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier" id="mwA_Y">doi</a>:<a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1111%2Fj.1467-9647.2005.00249.x" id="mwA_c">10.1111/j.1467-9647.2005.00249.x</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Teaching+Theology+and+Religion&amp;rft.atitle=Divine+therapy%3A+Teaching+reflective+and+meditative+practices&amp;r