SI">978-1-58062-884-6</a> p. 175</span></li><li about="#cite_note-72" id="cite_note-72"><a href="./Meditation#cite_ref-72" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-72" class="mw-reference-text">For a general overview see <i id="mwBSM">Beads of Faith: Pathways to Meditation and Spirituality Using Rosaries, Prayer Beads, and Sacred Words</i> by Gray Henry, Susannah Marriott 2008 <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt259" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"1-887752-95-1"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBSQ"/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" about="#mwt259" id="mwBSU">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt259" id="mwBSY"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/1-887752-95-1" title="Special:BookSources/1-887752-95-1" about="#mwt259" id="mwBSc">1-887752-95-1</a></span></li><li about="#cite_note-Vishnu-73" id="cite_note-Vishnu-73"><span rel="mw:referencedBy"><a href="./Meditation#cite_ref-Vishnu_73-0"><span class="mw-linkback-text">1 </span></a><a href="./Meditation#cite_ref-Vishnu_73-1"><span class="mw-linkback-text">2 </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-Vishnu-73" class="mw-reference-text"><i id="mwBSg">Meditation and Mantras</i> by Vishnu Devananda 1999 <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt260" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"81-208-1615-3"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBSk"/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" about="#mwt260" id="mwBSo">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt260" id="mwBSs"> 