ational Standard Book Number" about="#mwt410" id="mwBh4">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt410" id="mwBh8"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-1-56821-522-8" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-56821-522-8" about="#mwt410" id="mwBiA">978-1-56821-522-8</a> p. 45</span></li><li about="#cite_note-Kaplan,_A._1985-117" id="cite_note-Kaplan,_A._1985-117"><span rel="mw:referencedBy"><a href="./Meditation#cite_ref-Kaplan,_A._1985_117-0"><span class="mw-linkback-text">1 </span></a><a href="./Meditation#cite_ref-Kaplan,_A._1985_117-1"><span class="mw-linkback-text">2 </span></a><a href="./Meditation#cite_ref-Kaplan,_A._1985_117-2"><span class="mw-linkback-text">3 </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-Kaplan,_A._1985-117" class="mw-reference-text">Kaplan, A. (1985) <i id="mwBiE">Jewish Meditation: A Practical Guide,</i> New York Schocken Books.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-118" id="cite_note-118"><a href="./Meditation#cite_ref-118" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-118" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation book" about="#mwt422" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"last1":{"wt":"Scholem"},"first1":{"wt":"Gershom Gerhard"},"title":{"wt":"Major Trends in Jewish Mysticism"},"date":{"wt":"1961"},"publisher":{"wt":"Schocken Books"},"isbn":{"wt":"978-0-8052-1042-2"},"page":{"wt":"34"},"url":{"wt":"https://books.google.com/books?id=kD2y4wMOlAoC&amp;pg=PA34"},"language":{"wt":"en"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBiI">Scholem, Gershom Gerhard (1961). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=kD2y4wMOlAoC&amp;pg=PA34" id="mwBiM"><i id="mwBiQ">Major Trends in Jewish Mysticism</i></a>. Schocken Books. p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBiU"> </span>34. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standa