y Vincent W. Fallio 2006 <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt538" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"1-60021-247-6"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBxE"/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" about="#mwt538" id="mwBxI">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt538" id="mwBxM"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/1-60021-247-6" title="Special:BookSources/1-60021-247-6" about="#mwt538" id="mwBxQ">1-60021-247-6</a> p. 151</span></li><li about="#cite_note-163" id="cite_note-163"><a href="./Meditation#cite_ref-163" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-163" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation journal" about="#mwt540" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite journal","href":"./Template:Cite_journal"},"params":{"last":{"wt":"Feldman"},"first":{"wt":"G."},"title":{"wt":"Differential effects of mindful breathing, progressive muscle relaxation, and loving-kindness meditation on decentering and negative reactions to repetitive thoughts"},"journal":{"wt":"Behaviour Research and Therapy"},"year":{"wt":"2010"},"doi":{"wt":"10.1016/j.brat.2010.06.006"},"volume":{"wt":"48"},"issue":{"wt":"10"},"pages":{"wt":"1002–11"},"pmc":{"wt":"2932656"},"pmid":{"wt":"20633873"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBxU">Feldman, G. (2010). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2932656" id="mwBxY">"Differential effects of mindful breathing, progressive muscle relaxation, and loving-kindness meditation on decentering and negative reactions to repetitive thoughts"</a>. <i id="mwBxc">Behaviour Research and Therapy</i>. <b id="mwBxg">48</b> (10): 1002–11. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Digital_object_identifi